author: Subhajit Ganguly

resources.description: The dataset refers to water quality of river Damodar, Rupnarayan, Barakar, Konar, Jumar, Bokaro and Mahananda in 2008. The minimum, maximum and mean values of water quality parameters like Temperature, Dissolved Oxygen(D.O.), pH, Conductivity, Biochemical Oxygen Demand(B.O.D), Nitrate-N and Nitrite-N, Fecal Coliform and Total Coliform are given in the dataset. The data is sourced from Status of Water quality in India - 2008.
